'''''Mabata Bata''''', ni filime yerekana ikinamico ya [[Mozambike]] yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Sol de Carvalho ikaba yarayikoranye hamwe na Rodrigo Areias na Ricardo Freitas kuri Bando à parte Promarte Films<ref>https://mubi.com/films/mabata-bata</ref>.  Filime yakuwe mu nkuru ngufi “The Day Mabata Bata Exploded” yanditswe n'umwanditsi wa [[Mozambike]] Mia Couto<ref>http://africultures.com/films?no=19956</ref>.   Filime isobanura ubuzima bwa Azariya, umwungeri ukiri muto wimfubyi wita ku bushyo bwinka<ref>https://www.caribbeancreativity.nl/product/mabata-bata/</ref>. Nubwo arota kujya mwishuri, nyuma aherekejwe na Mabata Bata, impfizi nini yubushyo kugirango akomeze ubuzima bwe<ref>https://www.cinemazed.be/en/node/4705</ref><ref>https://www.degruyter.com/database/IABO/entry/iab201520150788/html</ref>. 

Amashusho ya firime ya TV yasohotse ku ya 30 Mata 2017 muri [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] na 1 Gicurasi 2017 muri [[Burezile|Berezile]]. Ku ya 30 Mutarama 2019<ref>https://supamodu.com/2019/africa/sol-de-carvalho-mabata-bata-2018/</ref>, iyi filime yasohotse mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam mu [[Buholandi]]<ref>https://www.everymancinema.com/film-info/mabata-bata</ref>. Filime yafatiwe hirya no hino muri Chibuto, Gaza na [[Mozambike|Mozambique]]<ref>https://cinemasdafrique.asso.fr/films/mabata-bata/</ref>. 

